features: Extra Electronic Organizer: Wedama toiletry bag for men is designed with electronic cable organizer compartment. The multiple mesh pockets and elastic loops are great for taking your cords, cables, USB drive, cellphone, charger, mouse, flash drive, and other accessories, which also protect your electronics accessories. Saying goodbye for messy cords, making your life happier.

Large Capacity: 9.5 x 4.8 x 6 inches. You can quickly put all the toiletries, hair wax, shower gel, shampoo, toothbrushes, razors, shaving cream, facial cleanser, general medicine and charging cords in the toiletry bag. The PU leather handle design is convenient for carrying and hanging. Suitable for men to use when traveling business and on trips.

Neat and Organized: The travel toiletry bag is designed with double zippers, allowing for an easy access to inner contents. The main compartment with a firmly magnetic buckle, increasing the closure of the toiletries bag. The 3 compartments with elastic straps can be hold bottles of various shapes and keep items upright, also putting cords and other items, keeping all your items organized.

High Quality Material: The surface of the men's travel toiletry bag is made of 600D Oxford cloth and PU, which is waterproof and dirt-proof. The stitching is woven with high-density double-needle thread to make the toiletry bag more sturdy and solid, increasing its durability. The bag interior is made of polyester, which is waterproof and easy to clean, even in the bathroom. There is no need to worry about getting wet or getting water in.

Travel Essentials: This portable travel toiletry bag is perfect for business trips, travel, gym, camping, and family outings. The design of Wedama toiletry bag is joined PU leather and embellished with metal elements, which makes it classic and stylish. Great gift choice for friends, boyfriends, and family for various occasions like birthdays, Father's Day, Christmas Day, and Valentine's Day.
